00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,560
Don't just stand there.

575
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:41,560
Sit.

576
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,240
Your needlework is artistry,

577
00:30:48,590 --> 00:30:50,680
but you've settled for scraps of work

578
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:51,880
at home these years.

579
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:53,240
It's such a waste.

580
00:30:54,310 --> 00:30:56,590
It's not easy for a woman to work outside.

581
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:59,070
Bringing you and your brother up

582
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,510
is satisfying enough for me.

583
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,790
But things are different now.

584
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:05,070
I'm the owner of Hualang Pavilion,

585
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:06,350
and your craft

586
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:08,070
needn't be confined at home.

587
00:31:08,830 --> 00:31:10,640
Would you like to help me

588
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:12,480
appraise embroidery?

589
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,520
Well...

590
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,550
I've been staying at home for years.

591
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,200
I'm afraid I'm not up to the task.

592
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,160
Don't worry, Mother.

593
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:23,590
This isn't nepotism,

594
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,830
but justice for your craft.

595
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:27,160
In this city,

596
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:29,000
there are many

597
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,340
brilliant women confined to their homes,

598
00:31:30,720 --> 00:31:32,510
their talents buried.

599
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,830
I hope you can discover more of them,

600
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:38,510
so that they won't be confined at home,

601
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:41,270
and their skills won't be buried in obscurity

602
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,830
but will be appreciated and remembered.

603
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:47,840
Ok.

604
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:49,550
With your assurance,

605
00:31:50,030 --> 00:31:51,830
I fear nothing.

606
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,320
Mother.

607
00:31:54,590 --> 00:31:55,550
So you'll do it?

608
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:06,190
Buddy!

609
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:13,480
The disadvantages of hereditary privilege?

610
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:15,400
After what happened at the Lu Mansion,

611
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,030
I'll channel my indignation into an essay.

612
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,160
What do you need?

613
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,920
I don't like

614
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,270
these plaque inscription drafts.

615
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:27,550
You should inscribe Hualang Pavilion.

616
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:31,300
(Hualang Pavilion)
I'll do it for you.

617
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,790
But as the owner,

618
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,790
don't you want to write it yourself?

619
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,400
I'm no calligrapher.

620
00:32:57,280 --> 00:33:00,460
♪Two swallows dart through the drizzle♪

621
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:03,640
♪A lonely shadow bars the window♪

622
00:33:04,810 --> 00:33:07,320
♪Thoughts lie concealed♪

623
00:33:07,740 --> 00:33:11,220
♪With no one to talk to♪

624
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,420
♪Things will be changed♪

625
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:18,660
♪At least, I have your shoulders♪

626
00:33:19,390 --> 00:33:21,590
♪Always by my side♪

627
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:25,940
♪Shining bright as fireflies♪

628
00:33:26,980 --> 00:33:29,840
♪Heart is like a web of silken twine♪

629
00:33:30,330 --> 00:33:33,140
♪Fate brews its sweet romance♪

630
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:36,340
(Pavilion)

631
00:33:37,090 --> 00:33:40,560
♪In pairs♪

632
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:44,930
♪Hearts share a silent thread♪

633
00:33:45,250 --> 00:33:48,280
♪Brief as dawn, vast as eternity♪

634
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,960
The calligraphy is excellent.

635
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:55,480
♪One glance spans eternity♪

636
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:58,620
(Hualang Pavilion)

637
00:34:06,140 --> 00:34:09,420
(Yin Residence)

638
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,440
Speaking of

639
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,670
Lady Yuanying,

640
00:34:13,110 --> 00:34:14,150
it's lucky that she met you.

641
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,840
Otherwise, who knows how long

642
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:17,940
she'd have been fooled by Lu Wencai.

643
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:19,550
She had no choice.

644
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:21,030
With her lowly status,

645
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,280
she couldn't get any help

646
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,720
to look for her brother.

647
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,960
She was easy prey for scoundrels.

648
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,760
Like me,

649
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,070
she was lucky to meet you

650
00:34:28,190 --> 00:34:29,320
when in a difficult situation.

651
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,360
If you put it that way,

652
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:33,800
I'm like a living Bodhisattva saving souls.

653
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,480
You're just so glib.

654
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,150
However,

655
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:43,030
this thing

656
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,710
inspires me.

657
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,480
Since ancient times,

658
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,630
men have been superior to women,

659
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:48,880
and the feudal ethics have been strict.

660
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:52,190
Many women in distress have nowhere to turn.

661
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:54,110
If Hualang Pavilion

662
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:56,550
could take on manageable commissions

663
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:59,230
to resolve their troubles,

664
00:34:59,510 --> 00:35:01,800
wouldn't that free more from their plights?

665
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:03,280
Good idea.

666
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,400
Let's make Hualang Pavilion

667
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:07,950
Women's Club,

668
00:35:08,070 --> 00:35:10,030
all members bound as sisters.

669
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:11,670
We can share joys

670
00:35:11,670 --> 00:35:12,920
in good times.

671
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:14,800
When we have difficulties,

672
00:35:15,110 --> 00:35:16,440
we can collaborate on plans

673
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:18,190
and devise solutions together.

674
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:19,630
That would be excellent.

675
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,620
We strike an instant chord.

676
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,190
Right, I have something else to ask you.

677
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:28,990
What is it?

678
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,320
I...

679
00:35:36,130 --> 00:35:37,960
Master Cui Li's handcrafted feng shui stone

680
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,590
was supposed to be obtained in six months.

681
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,320
Yet he graciously surrendered it to me.

682
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,000
What luck and joy!

683
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:47,660
(Five Blessings at the Door)

684
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,440
Gosh.

685
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:02,110
Bad news!

686
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:03,150
Master is here.

687
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:05,340
Give it to me.

688
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,210
- Master.
- Father.

689
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:47,800
Father,

690
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,840
I've gained new insights from history lately.

691
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:51,880
I'm looking forward to your guidance.

692
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:04,070
Come to my study at dusk.

693
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:05,680
Yes.

694
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,710
Sir, Master has departed.

695
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:33,480
I think you're overthinking this.

696
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:35,440
You were injured and lost your memory,

697
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,480
forgetting all your past.

698
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:37,960
As a result,

699
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,880
a lot of your sibling affection dissipated,

700
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:42,110
so to you, your brother

701
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,760
is no different from other men.

702
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:45,440
Later,

703
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:47,230
you pretended to be a couple

704
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:48,250
and got too close, which made you

705
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:50,670
develop strange feelings for him.

706
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,680
Is that really the case?

707
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,360
I don't think

708
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,440
it's a big deal.

709
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,370
Relax.

710
00:37:57,370 --> 00:37:58,420
Stop overthinking.

711
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,400
But honestly,

712
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:02,230
you two don't look alike.

713
00:38:02,670 --> 00:38:04,670
What if you're not biological siblings?

714
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:18,230
Once bathed in rain with the weeds,

715
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:21,190
now endure frost with the pines.

716
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,810
This is a poem by Master Linchuan.

717
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:29,400
When did I ever recite his poem?

718
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,360
If you like green bamboo,

719
00:38:32,510 --> 00:38:34,230
I'll have it planted in your courtyard.

720
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:35,600
No,

721
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:36,640
no need.

722
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:39,030
It's merely a fleeting thought.

723
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,230
Careful.

724
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:46,550
It's heavy.

725
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,960
Lady Mingshu.

726
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:56,590
Lady Yuanying,

727
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,400
what brings you here?

728
00:38:58,510 --> 00:39:00,190
Something just came to my mind.

729
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:01,760
I'm not sure if it will be helpful

730
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:02,710
for Mr. Su's case.

731
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,640
Go on.

732
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,710
I've been thinking about it recently,

733
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:07,510
and I recalled our maid mentioning

734
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:09,230
that after Mr. Su was taken,

735
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:12,030
Jian Jinhai, the owner of Jian's Gold Shop,

736
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:13,110
came to see my father

737
00:39:13,230 --> 00:39:14,510
and gave him a good scolding.

738
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:17,030
It seemed that he was defending Mr. Su.

739
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:20,190
I'm not sure if he holds any clues.

740
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:24,360
Looks like Jian Jinhai was close to Mr. Su.

741
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:26,150
I'll tell my brother.

742
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:28,070
And,

743
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:30,920
at the banquet,

744
00:39:31,110 --> 00:39:34,400
you hurt yourself to expose Lu Wencai.

745
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,710
Thank you very much.

746
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:38,920
I was trying to save myself.

747
00:39:39,710 --> 00:39:41,440
I owe it to you for this matter.

748
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:49,320
To conceive the great idea of Women's Club,

749
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:52,320
you're truly ingenious, kind-hearted,

750
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,190
and admirable.

751
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,880
Though bound to the Office,

752
00:39:58,550 --> 00:40:00,840
I'd like to contribute however I can.

753
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:02,630
I wonder what you...

754
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:04,830
Nothing would honor us more.

755
00:40:41,180 --> 00:40:46,180
(Unpolished Jade, Pure Gold)

756
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:23,150
Where am I?

757
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:53,590
It's him again.

758
00:42:15,110 --> 00:42:16,280
Who are you?

759
00:42:43,750 --> 00:42:46,300
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

760
00:42:46,300 --> 00:42:48,840
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

761
00:42:50,070 --> 00:42:52,720
♪As time quietly slips away♪

762
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:55,800
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

763
00:42:56,570 --> 00:42:59,050
♪May this heart stay true as the first day♪

764
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:02,330
♪I'll wait through blooms and dew♪

765
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:07,880
♪Let greed and wrath fade with the wind♪

766
00:43:09,050 --> 00:43:11,480
♪May life's towers stand tall♪

767
00:43:11,480 --> 00:43:13,970
♪With love that outlasts all♪

768
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:17,920
♪Together we'll traverse♪

769
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:21,100
♪Through grandeur and adversity♪

770
00:43:21,860 --> 00:43:24,320
♪When clarity arrives♪

771
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:27,730
♪Destiny's threads entwine,
Karma's path refines♪

772
00:43:28,320 --> 00:43:33,520
♪In glances back, our story's told♪

773
00:43:34,070 --> 00:43:37,420
♪If all scenes fade to view♪

774
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:40,350
♪Will you return♪

775
00:43:40,680 --> 00:43:43,440
♪Through years with sincere love♪

776
00:43:43,440 --> 00:43:46,600
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

777
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:50,170
♪Counting endless nights♪

778
00:43:50,170 --> 00:43:52,300
♪Yet never your♪

779
00:43:52,300 --> 00:43:58,390
♪Silhouette in sight♪

780
00:43:59,850 --> 00:44:02,820
♪If the moon above the sea is full♪

781
00:44:03,110 --> 00:44:05,900
♪Will you return♪

782
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:09,200
♪In years left, wait for me♪

783
00:44:09,360 --> 00:44:12,300
♪With a beginning and an end♪

784
00:44:12,570 --> 00:44:15,600
♪May time inscribe our names♪

785
00:44:15,860 --> 00:44:18,730
♪Where vows remain♪

786
00:44:19,050 --> 00:44:22,580
♪As if it were yesterday♪

